Runtime fallbacks and runtime functions:
// - src/runtime/runtime-intl.cc: RUNTIME_FUNCTION(Runtime_StringToLowerCaseIntl) and Runtime_StringToUpperCaseIntl: calls into ICU/Intl when needed and flattens inputs
// - src/runtime/runtime-strings.cc: RUNTIME_FUNCTION(Runtime_StringAdd): handles fallback string addition and returns NewConsString or copies. Contains checks for cons/sliced and flattening
// - src/builtins/string.tq: builtin StringSlowFlatten corresponds to String::SlowFlatten in C++ runtime
// - src/runtime/runtime-strings.cc also includes helpers that call isolate->factory()->NewConsString and flattening
